{"tid":1942023,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"唔好淨係掛住罵DearJane首新歌喇 入面有個黃嘅演員冇乜人識啊","createTime":"2020-03-24T20:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T19:29:51.000Z","uid":264783,"like":56,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"266c531326a9510074c0a2cd20d54d7ced3854f2","tid":1942023,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T20:37:50.000Z","msg":"與其用幾百頁去分析Dear Jane係咪黃，點解唔去留意吓佢首歌入面有個已經表左態嘅新進男演員 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">柯煒林</span></span> <br />\n先不論政治立場，香港演藝界已經係一敗塗地<br />\n難得今次DearJane請嘅男女演員都係黃<br />\n小薯茄係黃 參加八月五罷工就好多人知啦<br />\n但係男主角柯煒林早係6月12號已經係IG表咗態<br />\n大家係唔係應該比香港年輕一代嘅演員有成名嘅機會呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyOCCzA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyOCCzA.png&h=64759e83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希望大家唔好鬧佢po 得一張黑色相唔代表係乜<br />\n因為黃色圈係要擴大而唔係不斷審查 同時我哋唔會知道人哋係背後做咗幾多 最基本為咗香港演藝圈嘅重新起步<br />\n唔該首先行動，follow <a href=\"https://instagram.com/willallwailam?igshid=13hdxlyfy0bx4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fwillallwailam%3Figshid%3D13hdxlyfy0bx4&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=5599672d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/willallwailam?igshid=13hdxlyfy0bx4</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1803d363b3d61ab4d2550051c8847708c13f26cc","tid":1942023,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T20:39:18.000Z","msg":"向佐"},{"pid":"8a6e6922620445c0771e94474ed191067a4a2b80","tid":1942023,"uid":157994,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T21:53:00.000Z","msg":"邊有人care仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a528648ef509c5d17e387593f1d4a129059a97b","tid":1942023,"uid":176935,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T21:58:09.000Z","msg":"Dear Jane食屎啦"},{"pid":"11b93be56e6e201b4722c240ddd5eb48886e4f4f","tid":1942023